---
title: Cal Smart Szechuan Honey Shrimp and Salmon with Fluffy Rice, Carrots and Zucchini
description: Sweet and savoury meet in our honey shrimp, salmon and zucchini stir-fry. Bold soy, zesty green onions and fragrant honey lighten up this twist on a takeout favourite.

